================================================================
=== A. PARTITIONED — detach three months, one statement each
================================================================

--- month 2025-01 ---

$ psql -c "SELECT count(*) AS rows_in_this_partition FROM events_2025_01;"
 rows_in_this_partition 
------------------------
                 203855
(1 row)


$ psql -c "\timing on" -c "ALTER TABLE events DETACH PARTITION events_2025_01;"
Timing is on.
ALTER TABLE
Time: 2.312 ms

$ psql -c "SELECT count(*) AS rows_left_in_events FROM events;"
 rows_left_in_events 
---------------------
             2196145
(1 row)


--- month 2025-02 ---

$ psql -c "SELECT count(*) AS rows_in_this_partition FROM events_2025_02;"
