================================================================
=== B. FLAT TWIN — delete the same three months
================================================================

--- deleting [2025-01-01, 2025-02-01) ---

$ psql -c "SELECT count(*) AS rows_to_delete FROM events_flat WHERE occurred_at >= '2025-01-01' AND occurred_at < '2025-02-01';"
 rows_to_delete 
----------------
         203855
(1 row)


$ psql -c "\timing on" -c "DELETE FROM events_flat WHERE occurred_at >= '2025-01-01' AND occurred_at < '2025-02-01';"
